            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%8F%91%E7%83%AD%E5%8B%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE%E6%93%A6%E6%8B%AD%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%8F%91%E7%83%AD%E5%8B%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE%E6%93%A6%E6%8B%AD%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#儿童发热勿用酒精擦拭降温#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8D%A2%E5%AD%A3%E4%BA%86%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8D%A2%E5%AD%A3%E4%BA%86%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#换季了当心孩子感冒#</span></a> 医生介绍，因为儿童皮肤比较薄嫩，酒精容易通过皮肤的毛细血管进入体内，导致孩子出现急性酒精中毒。医生建议，儿童高热时要口服退热药物，大量喝温开水，减少衣物来帮助散热，用温热的毛巾擦拭手心、脚心、脖子、腋窝、大腿根等。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6OZQVBY" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
